headline: Stanley Black & Decker Announces 4th Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK), a worldwide leader in Tools and Outdoor, announced today that its Board of Directors approved a regular fourth quarter cash dividend of $0.83 per common share. The dividend is payable on Tuesday, December 16, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on Monday, December 1, 2025.

headline: Lincoln Electric Holdings (LECO) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Lincoln Electric (LECO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.35% and +1.91%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
